ActYukon Act
SubjectHon. C. Adèle Kent - Deputy Judge of the Supreme Court of Yukon ** Appointment **
PrecisOrder (1) appointing the Hon. C. ADÈLE KENT, a former Justice of the Court of the Queen's Bench of Alberta, to be a DEPUTY JUDGE of the SUPREME COURT OF YUKON; and (2) fixing her remuneration and allowances in accordance with the schedule.
